cu.explanation_en: Changing the remote S address from a string to a number will cause type mismatch errors during configuration parsing and prevent proper F1 interface connection.

du.explanation_en: Changing the remote N address from a string to a number will cause type mismatch errors during configuration parsing and prevent proper F1 interface connection.
du.explanation_zh: 將遠端 N 地址從字串改為數字會導致配置解析期間的類型不匹配錯誤，並阻止正確的 F1 介面連接。
